unto them; How is it that ye sought Me? Wist.ye 
not that I must be about my Father’s business ? And 
they understood not the saying which He spake unto 
them. But His mother kept all these sayings in her 
heart. And Jesus increased in wisdom and stature, 
and in favour with God and man. 





