that ye believe on Him Whom He hath sent. For 
the Bread of God is He Which cometh down from 
heaven, and giveth life unto the world. Then said 
they unto Him: tLord, evermore give us this bread. 
And Jesus said unto them: I am the Bread of Life; 
he that cometh to Me shall never hunger; and he 
that believeth on Me shall never thirst. All that the 
Father giveth Me shall come to Me; and him that 
