IN those days came John the Baptist, preaching 
in the wilderness of Judea, and saying: Repent ye, 
for the kingdom of heaven is at hand. I indeed 
baptize you with water unto repentance; but He that 
cometh after me is mightier than I, Whose shoes I 
am not worthy to bear; He shall baptize you with 
